  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become the Starborn Survivor!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The galaxy is under attack. You are the <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong>, an ancient robotic warrior, previously known as a Nova Sentinel, armed with forgotten technology, tasked with defending worlds from an alien invasion. In this <strong>debut game from our indie team</strong>, you’ll face relentless waves of enemies, uncover your mysterious origins, and upgrade your survival abilities.<i><u>  </u></i><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARLY ACCESS TITLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re launching <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong> in Early Access to build the best possible game with the help of our community. As a <strong>small, self-funded indie team</strong>, we believe that player feedback is essential to refining gameplay, balancing mechanics, and expanding content. Early Access allows us to iterate, experiment, and evolve based on real player experiences, ensuring that every update makes the game more engaging, challenging, and rewarding. Join us in shaping <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from our first <strong>three Cores</strong>, each with unique strengths:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defensive:</strong> Built to endure, this class excels at absorbing damage and protecting allies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mobility:</strong> Speed and agility define this style, allowing you to outmaneuver and outsmart enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aggressive:</strong> Overpower foes with raw firepower and relentless attacks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each style brings a different approach to the battlefield, letting you fight your way.<u><i> </i></u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with a basic set of tools, including <strong>shields, swords, and launchers</strong>!  Expand your capabilities as you play.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect attachments and upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn credits by defeating enemies to unlock more advanced equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with combinations to create a build that suits your style.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND THE COLONY</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The battle takes place on a single colony world, a hostile environment filled with alien threats. Master the terrain, adapt to the challenges, and prepare for intense battles against waves of enemies and powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LEARN, ADAPT, SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a starting point for what we hope will become an epic universe. While death is inevitable, each failure will teach you more about how to fight, survive, and dominate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to step into the fight and become the Starborn Survivor? <strong>The galaxy is counting on you</strong>.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become the Starborn Survivor!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The galaxy is under attack. You are the <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong>, an ancient robotic warrior, previously known as a Nova Sentinel, armed with forgotten technology, tasked with defending worlds from an alien invasion. In this <strong>debut game from our indie team</strong>, you’ll face relentless waves of enemies, uncover your mysterious origins, and upgrade your survival abilities.<i><u>  </u></i><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/a70066c05accbbf3724a47a28861ff63.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARLY ACCESS TITLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re launching <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong> in Early Access to build the best possible game with the help of our community. As a <strong>small, self-funded indie team</strong>, we believe that player feedback is essential to refining gameplay, balancing mechanics, and expanding content. Early Access allows us to iterate, experiment, and evolve based on real player experiences, ensuring that every update makes the game more engaging, challenging, and rewarding. Join us in shaping <strong>Starborn Survivor</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/0615fcb362edfc41ae145646060626a2.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from our first <strong>three Cores</strong>, each with unique strengths:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defensive:</strong> Built to endure, this class excels at absorbing damage and protecting allies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mobility:</strong> Speed and agility define this style, allowing you to outmaneuver and outsmart enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aggressive:</strong> Overpower foes with raw firepower and relentless attacks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each style brings a different approach to the battlefield, letting you fight your way.<u><i> </i></u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/ddb57a6120f3b2420bb2c92dce6b2a29.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with a basic set of tools, including <strong>shields, swords, and launchers</strong>!  Expand your capabilities as you play.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect attachments and upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn credits by defeating enemies to unlock more advanced equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with combinations to create a build that suits your style.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND THE COLONY</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/3dfb026af103e0f6c0a040fa1c09c97f.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The battle takes place on a single colony world, a hostile environment filled with alien threats. Master the terrain, adapt to the challenges, and prepare for intense battles against waves of enemies and powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LEARN, ADAPT, SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.poster.avif?t=1742594688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.webm?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843810/extras/cc1e307117393dde057b9dea6eed98fb.mp4?t=1742594688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a starting point for what we hope will become an epic universe. While death is inevitable, each failure will teach you more about how to fight, survive, and dominate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to step into the fight and become the Starborn Survivor? <strong>The galaxy is counting on you</strong>.</p>",
